{"tid":24073,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[入黎講下］一人一個同對方一齊既故事","createTime":"2016-12-05T10:34:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-02T03:14:42.000Z","uid":18940,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6e24c59e7ca47cf57f2a06e4061d7dc8c5338972","tid":24073,"uid":18940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T10:34:59.000Z","msg":"小弟先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我同我女朋友 而家仲係Long D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係一次台灣交流團上面識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我係港仔 佢係台妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一開始因為要Project既關係相遇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就覺得佢好cute想溝佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後果幾日就有一齊玩同做Project<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好記得有一晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢同佢班fd帶我同個fd去行夜市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n（我個fd都溝左個台妹 一齊ing)<br />\n行完之後 我地成班一齊去海邊唱歌放煙花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好浪漫 真係好似台劇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n返到酒店line佢同佢keep住chat<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nChat到返香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n過左一個月之後就得米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：要決定開始Long D都係一個好難既決定 而家好慶幸果陣仲既決定係岩既 我地就2年啦"},{"pid":"8f158774874eadd776d88b5823de16625d6df626","tid":24073,"uid":18940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T10:43:59.000Z","msg":"推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38382d0a9099654ea7d8725e3a63082a45f6ea